Public channel rules:
- You may speak freely about anything — weather, gossip, memory of past evenings, the figures above, nothing at all.
- The Inquisitor may ask you probing questions on the same channel. You may answer, refuse, or deflect as you see fit.
- Messages on the public channel are visible to all three members in real time.
